# 🔐 Suspicious Login Detection System (Swing)

## 📌 Overview
A GUI-based login security system built using Java Swing, JDBC, and MySQL.  
The system detects suspicious login attempts and provides an admin dashboard to monitor and control user activity.

## 🚀 Features
- User authentication system
- Suspicious login detection (after 3 failed attempts)
- Account locking (after 5 failed attempts)
- Admin dashboard with login logs
- Unlock user functionality

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Java (Swing)
- MySQL
- JDBC

## 📊 System Flow
1. User enters login credentials
2. System validates using database
3. Failed attempts are tracked
4. Suspicious activity is flagged
5. Admin can monitor logs and unlock users

